{"tid":644511,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"「足球小將」正名為「隊長小翼」？","createTime":"2018-04-27T09:31:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-30T08:08:48.000Z","uid":34409,"like":3,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"fa9c637721bf482408775902228ba9465a3aff6c","tid":644511,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T09:31:09.000Z","msg":"日本旅遊資訊網站「粹日本」（IKIDANE NIPPON）上周日在其Facebook專頁，刊出一篇關於日本東京都葛飾區之旅遊資訊時，將港人耳熟能詳的日本著名動畫《足球小將》寫為中國之譯名《隊長小翼》，結果遭到網民質疑，指「中港澳譯名係足球小將，而且係現在進行式。台灣譯名係足球小將-翼。幾時出現隊長小翼呢？」 <br />\n<br />\n「粹日本」專頁負責人今早回覆該名網民時指，「<span style=\"color: red;\">作品譯名按出版社集英社要求，現時香港譯名定為「隊長小翼」</span>；謝謝。」 <br />\n<br />\n《足球小將》作者為高橋陽一，於1981年開始連載，原作之日文名稱為《キャプテン翼》，英譯為《Captain Tsubasa》，香港一方獲得版權後，將名字改為《足球小將》，結果大受歡迎，成為幾代香港人的集體回憶。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/04-27-2018/45473\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F04-27-2018%2F45473&d=Cafjcg0goWczJSZ7u65licmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=455bf8f6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/04-27-2018/45473</a>"},{"pid":"cda0fb126406de0b3039a9bf63a2408f78c1dfad","tid":644511,"uid":127347,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T09:33:31.000Z","msg":"屌，美國隊長咩？<br />\n叫鋼門源三呀笨"},{"pid":"0195b5def7494ca34dad8e9012c8c63bffcc2bde","tid":644511,"uid":182930,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T09:34:11.000Z","msg":"去啦大胸翼，用衝力射球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"839bb9e4abdc7f904fe559131d6a8e09bbe0e09c","tid":644511,"uid":146467,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T09:34:29.000Z","msg":"好地地做乜要改-.-？"},{"pid":"b8743a1e7ca62e06d804fe99e3867c2411dde510","tid":644511,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T09:34:51.000Z","msg":"無曬霸氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1545a4a5ce34b9411581ab935ca7c5fb600ef3c","tid":644511,"uid":146